description: Relates a datatype that encodes a range of integers to the name of the person or organization who can use those ids constructed in that range to define new terms

example of usage:
Datatype: idrange:1
Annotations: 'has ID range allocated to': "Chris Mungall"
EquivalentTo: xsd:integer[> 2151 , <= 2300]

label: has ID range allocated to
